    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Secretions and excretions of protein fiber, of various compositions, from spiders and various insects. The fiber is used by the animals for cocoons, webs, transportation, nests, to catch or preserve prey, among other purposes.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
